blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: As a logistics and supply chain hub, FLS Hat Yai is located in the thriving business center of southern Thailand, strategically connected to Malaysia and the Southeast Asia region.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: Ms. Panadda Wichakul, Branch Manager Songkhla, will lead the Hat Yai team with her vision of constantly expanding and improving our services through effective vendor management.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: “Staffed by professionals who are familiar with local industries, regional vendors and partners, FLS Hat Yai customizes seamless, borderless services with competitive transportation costs that benefit our client’s global supply chains”, shared Francesco Josè Rivi, Managing Director, FLS Thailand.

blocks.name: core/gallery
core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: Please don’t hesitate to visit us for a coffee and a chat about your business at:

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: 599 Moo 1, 6/F Room HYI 6-A/2, Hat Yai Airport, Lopburi Rames Roads, T. Khuan Lang, A. Hat Yai Songkhla 90110, Thailand

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: Email: panadda@fls-group.com (Panadda Witchakul)
